    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors scoped as not-assessed consistent with MRL 2 and medium model influence designation. Validation output comparison demonstrates NIH predictions within 9.3% of benchmark experimental data across all five operating points with RH < 1 at all points. The UQ campaign embedded in VR-01 confirmed low parametric sensitivity of the hemolysis index. The assessment team concludes the CFD model has sufficient credibility to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device.",
